article_text: Children at Immanuel Presbyterian Church in Milwaukee dressed in first-century garb and proceeded through the sanctuary waving their palms and leading the congregation to the Upper Room Meal. According to tradition, the Last Supper took place in a room in Jerusalem that’s referred to as the Upper Room.
